            "title": "Upgrade CEO: $165 Million Raise Likely 'Last Pre-IPO'",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div class=\"akcelo-wrapper akcelo-video media--169\" style=\"width:100%\"><div class=\"border:solid 1px #C0C0C0\" id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\" video-id=\"k3c6WoDh3FhCawE2rDu\"><div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta content=\"Upgrade CEO: k3c6WoDh3FhCawE2rDu65 Million Raise Likely 'Last Pre-IPO'\" itemprop=\"name\"/><meta content='Neobank startup Upgrade closed a k3c6WoDh3FhCawE2rDu65 million funding round at a $7.3 billion valuation, which CEO Renaud Laplanche says is likely the last ahead of an IPO. Laplanche joins Caroline Hyde and Ed Ludlow on \"Bloomberg Tech.\"\n' itemprop=\"description\"/><meta content=\"2025-10-16T22:13:09+02:00\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/><meta content=\"/images/mtnewswires/A3478414.png\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/><meta content=\"https://geo.dailymotion.com/player/x80uo.html?video=k3c6WoDh3FhCawE2rDu\" itemprop=\"embedUrl\"/></div></div></div>\n               Neobank startup Upgrade closed a $165 million funding round at a $7.3 billion valuation, which CEO Renaud Laplanche says is likely the last ahead of an IPO. Laplanche joins Caroline Hyde and Ed Ludlow on \"Bloomberg Tech.\"<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51365833');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
